author: jtyberg
msg: navigator.camera.getPicture(success, fail, { destinationType:DestinationType.DATA_URL }); returns base64 encoded image.
navigator.camera.getPicture(success, fail, { destinationType:DestinationType.FILE_URI }); returns image URI.

author: jtyberg
msg: Add ScriptEngine and callback methods to PhoneGapExtension to provide a central mechanism for invoking callbacks.
Add CommandResult.Status.INPROGRESS so plugins can delay callback invocation.
JS callbacks print out exception message instead of generic JSON error.

author: mwbrooks
msg: Fix generate-cod-name to support a default name.
When an application name contains no special character,
then the regex would return blank instead of the app name.
